  <excerpt>Short description for second post</excerpt>
  <content>&lt;div class="heading-wrapper" style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; position: relative;" data-heading-level="h2"&gt;
&lt;h2 id="why-choose-aspnet-core" class="heading-anchor" style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; margin: 32px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-size: clamp(1.59375rem, 18.7895px + 1.39803vw, 2.125rem); line-height: 1.3; margin-inline-start: -1.875rem; padding-inline-start: 1.875rem;"&gt;Why choose ASP.NET Core?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; margin: 1rem 0px 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word;"&gt;Millions of developers use or have used&amp;nbsp;&lt;a style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;" href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/aspnet/overview" data-linktype="absolute-path"&gt;ASP.NET 4.x&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;to create web apps. ASP.NET Core is a redesign of ASP.NET 4.x, including architectural changes that result in a leaner, more modular framework.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; margin: 1rem 0px 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word;"&gt;ASP.NET Core provides the following benefits:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; margin: 16px 0px 16px 38px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;"&gt;
&lt;li style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; list-style: disc; color: #161616; font-family: 'Segoe UI', SegoeUI, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"&gt;A unified story for building web UI and web APIs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; list-style: disc; color: #161616; font-family: 'Segoe UI', SegoeUI, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"&gt;Architected for testability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; list-style: disc; color: #161616; font-family: 'Segoe UI', SegoeUI, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;a style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;" href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/aspnet/core/razor-pages/?view=aspnetcore-8.0" data-linktype="relative-path"&gt;Razor Pages&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;makes coding page-focused scenarios easier and more productive.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; list-style: disc; color: #161616; font-family: 'Segoe UI', SegoeUI, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;a style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;" href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/aspnet/core/blazor/?view=aspnetcore-8.0" data-linktype="relative-path"&gt;Blazor&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;lets you use C# in the browser alongside JavaScript. Share server-side and client-side app logic all written with .NET.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; list-style: disc; color: #161616; font-family: 'Segoe UI', SegoeUI, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"&gt;Ability to develop and run on Windows, macOS, and Linux.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; list-style: disc; color: #161616; font-family: 'Segoe UI', SegoeUI, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"&gt;Open-source and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;" href="https://live.asp.net/" data-linktype="external"&gt;community-focused&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; list-style: disc; color: #161616; font-family: 'Segoe UI', SegoeUI, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"&gt;Integration of&amp;nbsp;&lt;a style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;" href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/aspnet/core/blazor/?view=aspnetcore-8.0" data-linktype="relative-path"&gt;modern, client-side frameworks&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and development workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; list-style: disc; color: #161616; font-family: 'Segoe UI', SegoeUI, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"&gt;Support for hosting Remote Procedure Call (RPC) services using&amp;nbsp;&lt;a style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;" href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/aspnet/core/grpc/?view=aspnetcore-8.0" data-linktype="relative-path"&gt;gRPC&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; list-style: disc; color: #161616; font-family: 'Segoe UI', SegoeUI, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"&gt;A cloud-ready, environment-based&amp;nbsp;&lt;a style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;" href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/aspnet/core/fundamentals/configuration/?view=aspnetcore-8.0" data-linktype="relative-path"&gt;configuration system&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; list-style: disc; color: #161616; font-family: 'Segoe UI', SegoeUI, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"&gt;Built-in&amp;nbsp;&lt;a style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;" href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/aspnet/core/fundamentals/dependency-injection?view=aspnetcore-8.0" data-linktype="relative-path"&gt;dependency injection&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; list-style: disc; color: #161616; font-family: 'Segoe UI', SegoeUI, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"&gt;A lightweight,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a style="box-sizing: inherit; outline-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;" href="https://github.com/aspnet/benchmarks" data-linktype="external"&gt;high-performance&lt;/a&gt;, and modular HTTP request pipeline.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</content>
